{"tid":2036591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國或下月中重開所有店舖 美提早禁曾到巴西人士入境","createTime":"2020-05-26T14:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T14:19:17.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b014a8205186d7fadaa926e3dac5fb4589180737","tid":2036591,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"英國或下月中重開所有店舖 美提早禁曾到巴西人士入境<br />\n2020-05-26 HKT 11:49<br />\n<br />\n美國約翰霍普金斯的統計顯示，全球累計接近550萬人感染新型冠狀病毒，34萬6千多人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜說，可能在下月中重開所有店舖；一段時間遙距辦公的俄羅斯總統普京，返回克里姆林宮開會。<br />\n<br />\n不過，巴西疫情未受控，美國提早實施禁止14日內到過巴西的旅客入境的措施。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528376-20200526.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528376-20200526.htm&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=e8d6595e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528376-20200526.htm&h=8e2ea0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528376-20200526.htm</a>"}]}